s, destroy\ndisks into spheroids, these results indicate that spiral galaxies cannot have\ngrown only by a succession of minor mergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2007 14:04:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Oct 2007 15:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
